title: No risk of economic stall seen in China (The Central People's Government of the People's ...
text: ( Source : The Central People's Government of the People's Republic of China ) Fluctuations in third quarter economic indicators do not mean that China is suffering an economic downturn. There are no risks of an economic stall in China.
